# Project Context

## Project Type
Static website built with Pelican (Python static site generator) and TailwindCSS.

## Design System
- Reference: `design_brief.json` for all design specifications
- Color palette: Blue accent (#1E88E5), high contrast AA/AAA
- Typography: Serif headings, neutral sans body (18px base, 1.6 leading)
- Layout: 12-column grid, max-width 1200px, responsive breakpoints
- Spacing: 4px (xxs) to 48px (xxl) scale

## Code Style
- Python: Follow PEP 8
- Jinja2 templates: Use 2-space indentation
- HTML: Semantic HTML5, accessibility-first
- CSS: TailwindCSS utility classes, custom config for design tokens

## Key Components
- Header: Sticky navigation with logo, primary nav, utilities
- Footer: Quick links, social icons, legal, signature
- Article cards: Kicker, title, excerpt, media, tag
- Forms: Netlify Forms compatible (netlify attribute)

## Content Structure
- Articles: Markdown files in `content/articles/`
- Pages: Markdown files in `content/pages/`
- Work experience: Custom page type
- Contact form: HTML form with Netlify attributes

## Important Files
- `pelicanconf.py`: Main Pelican configuration
- `tailwind.config.js`: TailwindCSS design tokens
- `themes/aquiles_theme/`: Custom theme templates

